              </p>
              <span class="project-card__meta">Rol — [lead projectmanager]</span>
            </article>

            <article class="project-card">
              <span class="project-card__num">04 · Event</span>
              <h3>[Project titel]</h3>
              <p>
                [Placeholder beschrijving — event of bruiloft. Van concept tot productie,
